type="local"
href="jms-00KI.xml"
addr="jms-00KI"
title="Closure of functions under identity and composition">identity function</fr:link> is an <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00MO.xml"
addr="jms-00MO"
title="Injection">injection</fr:link> and the <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00IN.xml"
addr="jms-00IN"
title="Relational composite">composition</fr:link> of <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00MO.xml"
addr="jms-00MO"
